nodes.text: Air Commodore was a title held by the Utai Senin Vant, who led the Utapau Skyforce—planetary defense force of the Utai and Pau'an homeworld Utapau—during the Clone Wars.

The title of air commodore was first used in the current canon in the 2018 reference book Star Wars: Complete Vehicles. The title was originally created for the 2005 Star Wars Legends reference book Star Wars: Revenge of the Sith Incredible Cross-Sections, which was written by Curtis Saxton.
